# LSP custom remaps

## Auto-complete
<C-n>      next item
<C-p>      previous item
<C-y>      confirm
<C-e>      close
<C-space>  complete
<C-b>      scroll down docs
<C-f>      scroll up docs

## Go to functions
gD         go to declaration
gd         go to definition
gr         go to references
gi         go to implementation

## Diagnostics
<space>q   set diagnostics in local list

## Float
K          display info
<C-k>      display signature help
<space>e   diagnostics

## Actions
<space>rn  rename
<space>ca  code action
<space>f   formatting

## Snippets
<C-j>      jump backwards
<C-k>      jump forward or expand
